abstract.gco:CharacterString: This polygon data layer represents tax parcels for Door County, Wisconsin in 2015. The dataset was originally published by the Door County Real Property Listing Office in 2015.[The Tax Parcel map of Door County, Wisconsin. This was derived from a variety of source maps including survey plats, deed descriptions, subdivision maps, certified survey maps, easements, and right-of-way plats. These source materials were of several different scales and were from dates ranging from the late 1800's to the present. This map provides a useful representation of the geometry and topology of tax parcels and is suitable for its intended purpose. It is not, however, meant to be used for the determination of land ownership and interest descriptions contained in individual deeds.]

purpose.gco:CharacterString:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This infromation is intended to be used by other County Departments and the general public as a base layer for showing parcel ownership and as an index to other attributes associated with tax parcels.]

measureDescription.gco:CharacterString: [Data set is topologically structured polygon data.]
[To the best knowledge of the Door County Real Property Listing Department, this theme includes all tax parcels in Door County, WI]
[Real Property Listing Department generates reports for verification on all entered changes.]

[Tax parcels (except building condos) were entered by coordinate geometry techniques fitted to section corner control. The horizontal positional accuracy for the parcel data is estimated at +/- 5 feet. Parcel mapping can be compared against measurement information contained in original source documents (deeds, subdivision plats, and CSMs). Individual Condo Unit Tax Parcels were placed within the Condo Plat property, but size and location of individual condos were digitized arbitrarily to provide a reference to within the Platted Property level only.]
